16:50.040 --> 16:53.580
shower you with unconditional love.

16:56.360 --> 16:57.950
When does that start?

16:58.590 --> 17:00.190
So needy.

17:04.760 --> 17:06.590
Come to Mommy.

17:08.650 --> 17:10.660
It's okay, go ahead.

17:18.070 --> 17:20.070
Oh, my son.

17:22.470 --> 17:24.480
Oh, my mother.

17:25.450 --> 17:27.430
Oh, my God.

