It's the hard-knock life for us

17:59.240 --> 18:02.580
It's the hard-knock life for us

18:02.580 --> 18:05.670
'Stead of treated, we get tricked

18:05.670 --> 18:09.070
'Stead of kisses, we get kicked

18:09.070 --> 18:11.390
It's the hard-knock life

18:11.390 --> 18:14.900
Got no folks to speak of so

18:14.900 --> 18:18.100
It's the hard-knock row we hoe

